---
// How It's Created Section (AI Agents)
---

<div id="how-it-works" class="bg-base-200 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">How It's Created</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-base-content/70 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Reports are automatically generated each month by a director agent that coordinates four specialized agents. They collect data from GitHub, write summaries for different audiences, and ensure quality.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8">
      <!-- Researcher Agent -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl border-t-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Researcher</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mb-4">
            Data collection specialist. Navigates GitHub APIs, parses repository activity, and extracts structured information from multiple sources.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/agents/researcher" class="btn btn-xs btn-outline btn-primary">View Instructions</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Summary Writer Agent -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl border-t-4 border-primary">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Summary Writer</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mb-4">
            Communication specialist. Translates technical jargon into accessible language, focuses on business impact, and writes for non-technical audiences.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/agents/summary" class="btn btn-xs btn-outline btn-primary">View Instructions</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Technical Writer Agent -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl border-t-4 border-cyan-500">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-cyan-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Technical Writer</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mb-4">
            Developer documentation specialist. Maintains technical accuracy, organizes code changes by repository, and preserves implementation details.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/agents/technical" class="btn btn-xs btn-outline btn-primary">View Instructions</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Report Fixer Agent -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl border-t-4 border-amber-500">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Report Fixer</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mb-4">
            Quality assurance specialist. Audits reports against style guidelines, detects inconsistencies, and applies surgical fixes to maintain standards.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/agents/report-fixer" class="btn btn-xs btn-outline btn-primary">View Instructions</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-lg p-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
        </svg>
        <div class="text-base-content/80">
          <p class="mb-2">This is an experimental system still in development.</p>
          <p class="mb-0">If you spot inaccuracies, please <a href="https://github.com/greymass/reporter/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-primary">open an issue on GitHub</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
